---
title: Portobello Burgers with Avocado, Caramelized Onions, and Spicy Mayo
description: Juicy portobellos are so hearty, they make the perfect vegetarian “burger”. Seared and finished with balsamic vinegar, these portobellos are served with caramelized onions, mashed avocado, and our favorite condiment: spicy mayo. A side salad rounds out this hearty summer meal.
